Package org.odpi.openmetadata.frameworks.openmetadata.properties.digitalbusiness

Class DigitalProductProperties

java.lang.Object
org.odpi.openmetadata.frameworks.openmetadata.properties.ClassificationProperties
org.odpi.openmetadata.frameworks.openmetadata.properties.digitalbusiness.DigitalProductProperties
public class DigitalProductProperties extends ClassificationProperties
DigitalProductProperties describes the properties that describe a digital product. It is typically attached to a solution component, but it can be attached to any referenceable.
